snippet.title: HAVENLESS Character Introduction third - Noah
snippet.description:
We're proud to announce the official global release [Havenless]!
(Google Play&App Store One-Link)
https://havenless.page.link/Banner


🚨:  Time for Noah's introduction! I met him by chance in the streets. Wanna hear what happened to us that night?


"So I'm infected, right?"
The story of a girl infected with a mysterious virus devastating the world.

#Havenless #Lucydream #otomegames
